			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Dear Mage Compendium,
<br />

<br />
Everyone who reads this, this is not really a rant. This is just a view, just something that set me off earlier, something that set off much hate that I felt a long time ago, and now it’s back again. Before I begin I’d like to list what this thread is NOT, as to not waste your time.
<br />

<br />
1. This is not an EverQuest rant.
<br />
2. This is not a political rant.
<br />

<br />
No, this is a rant about people in our everyday lives.
<br />

<br />
As some of you know. When I was younger I was picked on a lot because of my weight. I was called names, and I held it in for a long time. Eventually I cracked and my mom pulled my out of school, and I locked myself away from the world for a long time. I’ve since then broken out, I get out more, exercise more, etc.
<br />

<br />
But this thread is not about me this time. It’s about a friend of mine in EverQuest, and her friends in real life. Some I’ve come to know on places like AOL, since I retired from EverQuest.
<br />

<br />
She is in fact a good friend of mine. We duo’ed together on the Tunare server. I still talk to her and her friends on AIM now and then.
<br />

<br />
I was on AIM earlier and one of her friends where on. So I sent an IM saying the basic, everyday, “Hi! ^_^” and me and this girl talked for about 3 minutes… Later I found out this wasn’t the person I was talking to, that it was her friends, friend. And she was messing around on her SN.
<br />

<br />
She talked to me a bit and I get…
<br />

<br />
Her: So yeah, you see Traci on lately?
<br />
Me: Yeah, she was on a little while ago.
<br />
Her: You ever see Traci?
<br />
Me: Nope, why?
<br />
Her: She’s ugly.
<br />
Me: Wtf, who is this?
<br />
Her: Falicia
<br />
Me: Wtf, you have no ****ing right to call my friends ugly!
<br />

<br />
After I continued to curse this dumb bitch out. I’m usually a very calm person. But this set me off… Everything that happened to me from when I was a little boy, all the way until now… Just came to mind. And my hate rose. My mind went into a pure hateful rage. And I blocked this dumb shit before I said anything else. I was feeling my depression coming back. And I fought with it, and I currently still am fighting it.
<br />

<br />
My question to this dumb stupid ass world, is WHY THE HELL DO YOU THINK YOU HAVE THE FUCKING RIGHT TO JUDGE SOMEONE! YOU ARE THE UGLY ONE!
<br />

<br />
Why!? What the fuck is the point of saying someone is ugly? If you don’t like the way someone looks, keep it to yourself! It’s dumb ass people like this that makes me forsaken my generation of human beings! This is why I want NOTHING to do with them!
<br />

<br />
These people!… I don’t even know if I should call them people… Are PART OF THE REASON IN THE DECLINE OF THIS COUNTRY! People grow depressed when you say shit like this… And sometimes it goes through their entire lives! WHY THE FUCK DON’T YOU PEOPLE REALIZE THIS!?
<br />

<br />
You rip from people their self-confidence! You rip from them their souls and spirits! You kill them!…
<br />

<br />
This is what causes people to go over edge. This is what causes suicide. This is what causes many of the dysfunctional shit in the world today.
<br />

<br />
I’m not directing this at everyone. Just the people who are guilty of this crime…
<br />

<br />
If you are the people… Just remember the words from this song…
<br />

<br />
I can see through you, see to the real you, because inside you’re ugly, ugly like me.
<br />

<br />
That is all.<br />_________________<br />||Magician Master Sithro||Paladin Artavius Artimus||Rogue Sevian Daggerstorm||</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
