				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">There are many reasons why someone would say that someone is "ugly", "stupid", "fat" etc.
<br />

<br />
It usually has a lot to do with maturity and also insecurity.
<br />

<br />
People who are trying to put someone else down are usually insecure about themselves in some way so they try to point out others' "flaws" so you don't notice their own flaws.
<br />

<br />
Sometimes it's even a psychotic power-play.  People will try to make you feel this and feel that, but only you have the power to not feel.  I always look at the source of the slur, and that's enough for me.  Chalk it up to ignorance.
<br />

<br />
I don't know if this helps any, but people really can be cruel sometimes.
<br />

<br />
But, for every 1 of those people, there are 10 of us that are not.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
