				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Music. Art. Love. Family. Generosity. Charity. 
<br />

<br />
These are not fiction. Humanity has a long way to go to free itself from the chains of our history: hate, greed, selfishness, arrogance, conceit, violence.
<br />

<br />
But there is hope. There <span style="font-style: italic">is</span> a better, cleaner, higher state for us to aspire to.
<br />

<br />
The very fact of your outrage provides evidence of this. It is very easy to be locked into a cold, cynical and bleak outlook. Every day is a challenge to rise above the baser aspects of your being, every good deed - no matter hwo small - adds to the global goodwill potential. Every one of us fails, but every one of us can and does rise above in a thousand tiny ways every day.
<br />

<br />
Have hope, live well, spread joy.<br />_________________<br /><A HREF="http://pub44.ezboard.com/fsilverangel89587frm56">Inspiration</A></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
